languages.text: "Я — соглядатай?! Все видели, как я убивал ложноверцев. А вот где ты был{mf||а} в этот момент?"
"A spy? Me? Everyone saw me killing the false believers. But where were you while I was doing that?"

languages.text: "Ein Spion? Ich? Alle haben gesehen, wie ich die Ungläubigen getötet habe. Aber wo wart Ihr, während ich das getan habe?"
languages.original_text: "A spy? Me? Everyone saw me killing the false believers. But where were you while I was doing that?"

traits.locale_text: "Ein Spion? Ich? Jeder hat doch gesehen, wie ich die falschen Gläubigen getötet habe. Wo wart Ihr, während ich das getan habe, frage ich mich?"

languages.text: « Moi ? Un espion ? Tous m'ont vu tuer les faux croyants... Où étiez-vous, quand j'accomplissais cette tâche ? »
languages.original_text: "A spy? Me? Everyone saw me killing the false believers. But where were you while I was doing that?"

traits.locale_text: « Moi ? Un espion ? Tous ont pu voir qui tuait les faux croyants... Où étiez-vous, quand j'accomplissais cette tâche ? »

languages.text: “间谍？你说我？我杀了那些伪神的信徒，所有人都看到了。可我杀人的时候，你又在什么地方？”
languages.original_text: "A spy? Me? Everyone saw me killing the false believers. But where were you while I was doing that?"

traits.locale_text: “间谍？你说我？我杀了那些伪神的信徒，所有人都看到了。可话说回来，我杀人的时候，你又在什么地方？”

languages.text: 「スパイ？俺が？皆、偽信者を殺す様子を見ていた。それで、お前はその時どこにいた？」
languages.original_text: "A spy? Me? Everyone saw me killing the false believers. But where were you while I was doing that?"

traits.locale_text: 「スパイ？俺が？皆、偽信者を殺す様子を見ていた。それで、お前はその時どこにいた？」

languages.text: «¿Espía? ¿Yo? Todos vieron cómo mataba a los falsos creyentes. ¿Dónde estabas cuando estaba haciéndolo?».
languages.original_text: "A spy? Me? Everyone saw me killing the false believers. But where were you while I was doing that?"

traits.locale_text: «¿Espiando? ¿Yo? Todos vieron cómo mataba a los falsos creyentes. Dónde estabas cuando estaba haciéndolo?».

languages.text: "Casus mu? Ben mi? İnançlı numarası çekenleri sağ bırakmadığıma herkes şahit. O sırada sen nerelerdeydin?"
languages.original_text: "A spy? Me? Everyone saw me killing the false believers. But where were you while I was doing that?"

traits.locale_text: "Casus mu? Ben mi? Herkes benim sapkınları nasıl öldürdüğümü gördü. O sırada sen nerelerdeydin?"
